Home Security






Home Security Systems for Your Peace of Mind
 
A-A Lock & Alarm Inc installs the very latest in home security systems to give you the peace of mind that you deserve in your home. Whether you have already been a victim of a burglary or break-in or you never want to become a victim, we have alarm systems and high-tech equipment to keep you, your family, and your assets safe. With A-A Lock & Alarm Inc, there are no contracts and no hidden fees!
We offer advanced home security services, including the following:

System Removal
System Transfer
System Change
System Installations
New Home and Remodel Installations
And more!

The fact that we have over 60 years in the industry has earned us a top spot in the area, and we are familiar with all the latest technology in security systems and surveillance for both businesses and homes. From our family to your family, we will do whatever it takes to make you feel safe and at home. Call us today for a free estimate. Make sure to ask us about how we can lower your homeowners’ or renters’ insurance premiums!
Make sure to ask us about how we can lower your homeowners’ or renters’ insurance premiums!



Bump Key
Although our home security systems and locks are meant to keep intruders out of our homes, determined intruders can often find a way around them. One of the tricks they use is called lock bumping. Lock bumping is a widely known industry problem, and we have enlisted the top home security brands to help prevent lock bumping from occurring.
Lock bumping refers to the act of creating specially cut keys, also known as “bump keys,” to break into a home or business.  Bump keys can defeat tumbler door locks and conventional pin locks as well. Those performing the key bumping will then use the bump key, otherwise known as a “999 key,” with another object to force the lock open.
Kwikset offers the high-security ANSI Grade 1 980 Deadbolt which features SmartKey™ technology and BumpGuard™. The Kwikset SmartKey™ and BumpGuard™ technology give you the ability to re-key your lock in less than 30 seconds while still giving you superior key bumping security. Rather than replacing the entire lock to prevent a break-in, all you need to do is replace the key – saving you time, worry and money.



We Can Help with the Following Security Systems:

Security Cameras
Alarm Systems
Video Verification
Monitoring

Check with local agencies regarding codes for video verification & permits. We can help!







