A-A Lock & Alarm Inc - Menlo Park, CA - Why Us?























































Why Us?






Why Choose A-A Lock & Alarm Inc?
 
With our over six decades in the industry, we have become one of the leading one-stop security companies in the San Jose, CA area. Our team of technicians is highly trained with years of combined experience and extreme attention to detail. With A-A Lock & Alarm Inc, you get all the security and locksmith services you need for your home or business from one highly experienced company – making it easier to feel safe and secure no matter where you are. We can help you secure your family and pets, even watching your home remotely.
Unlike many other companies in the area, we have never hired subcontractors to do our work for us because we want to ensure that everything is done perfectly. From our 32-vehicle fleet to our 30 dedicated technicians, we want to always give you the best experience possible with us through friendly and prompt services. In addition, we can help with the following:
• Insurance requirements
 • Government regulations
 • HIPAA
We can help you lower your homeowners’ or renters’ insurance premiums. Ask us for more details today.

